# replace treehouse data
implemented dataUtilities/TCGA_Target_GTex.py.

differnces from Treehouse version

1. does not map genes ids to hugo
There are some ensemble gene ids that map to mulitple hugo genes.

2. tree house version gene expression version. I think this is becuase they select the set of gene ids that are common or becuause of the mapping issue

3. I found it hard to read the https://github.com/rcurrie/tumornormal/blob/master/ingest.ipynb source code. Lot of tick pandas

4. I wanted to a python script version so that I could easily include the load functionaly in other projects
